this morning to inform his results.

107
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:01,390
He made it into the top ten of his class

108
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:03,030
on his final exam this time.

109
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:05,870
Your dad said

110
