137
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:25,630
I just feel that since
the holiday is coming,

138
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,110
I want to have dinner with you.

139
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:29,460
What would you like to eat? 
It'll be my treat.

140
