157
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,540
They really like you.

158
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:20,910
Just go.

159
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,350
I'm going home soon.

160
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:23,390
Go on.

161
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:26,470
-I'm off now.
-Bye bye.

162
