174
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:22,550
You overslept every day
since the summer break started.

175
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,470
I don't know what you're doing at night.

176
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:26,870
All right, I'm up.

177
